后裔。明太祖朱元璋洪武年间，破锅杜氏流芳公一支由山西洪洞迁居河南府渑池县坻坞西村，成为渑池杜氏之祖。期望至宋代后成为庶民百姓的杜氏子孙能以天下兴亡为己任，为中华民族伟大复兴贡献力量。\n\n\n\n大殿内：\n\n## 木本水源\n\n注：此匾额位于宗祠大殿灵楼上方，“文化大革命”时期毁掉。2008年复制。木质黑底，阴刻金字。\n\n\n\n### 4. 宗祠内其他文字\n\n明敕赐义民临泉杜公真金墓\n\n生于嘉靖二十二年\n\n卒于万历四十七年\n\n不孝男杜三光杜三乐\n\n侄男杜三元\n\n孙杜从龙杜耀龙杜化龙杜飞龙\n\n杜腾龙\n\n侄杜□杜□\n\n侄孙杜乘龙\n\n玄孙杜由□杜为□\n\n\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_1397_1284_1827_2280.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"21%\" /></div>\n", "isStart": false, "isEnd": true, "images": {"imgs/img_in_image_box_1397_1284_1827_2280.jpg": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//e3d5f402-52d7-45d4-873a-01a4e28db290/markdown_0/imgs/img_in_image_box_1397_1284_1827_2280.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A31%3A11Z%2F-1%2F%2F1b7655e1c63aa82fec39da8ecedb5a8268e7afd3d643f1b7e232b4b1caafcec5"}}, "outputImages": {"layout_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//e3d5f402-52d7-45d4-873a-01a4e28db290/layout_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A31%3A12Z%2F-1%2F%2Fe2fa9af50ab47e16cda19b17cbfbf0d8c45ffdb44308668a8c605fba9529fabb", "region_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//e3d5f402-52d7-45d4-873a-01a4e28db290/region_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A31%3A12Z%2F-1%2F%2F7f4c34c86e2e86e1d27945d88d35d661860662d7602cb5de90e9f156020e546d", "overall_ocr_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//e3d5f402-52d7-45d4-873a-01a4e28db290/overall_ocr_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A31%3A12Z%2F-1%2F%2F7ba5847c182902fd80b0907cf59e429f75d0ff2038bfaf87c67f321f2fc618a5", "layout_order_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//e3d5f402-52d7-45d4-873a-01a4e28db290/l